title: Mathematical Unlimited v1.0.1

---VERSION WITHOUT ADS---

Are you tired of all the games with simple puzzles?
Do you want to go back to the days of retro?
Have you always wanted to save the princess?

You have a unique chance to play a game that will brighten your time on the tram, a lecture or a line for the clinic.
The main advantages are:
1) 18 levels with different difficulty
2) The endless mode
3) The unique layout

Ready for a challenge?
Download our application, complete a tutorial that will teach you the rules of the game and have fun forever!
